&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Buongiorno&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;questa non √® l‚Äôennesima newsletter per fare di pi√π:&lt;strong&gt; √® per stare meglio.&lt;/strong&gt;‚Äã&lt;br&gt;benvenuti/e nello spazio dove parliamo di digital detox: &lt;strong&gt;vita vera prima degli schermi.&lt;/strong&gt;‚Äã&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;Per vivere (non solo sopravvivere)&lt;/strong&gt; tra notifiche, email e chat infinite e intelligenza artificiale.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;Piccoli passi, grandi cambiamenti.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Ecco le tre cose di oggi.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;unordered_list&quot; style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;list_item&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Grazie davvero per i vostri feedback. &lt;strong&gt;Mi hanno aiutato tanto. Sono molto grato.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;‚Äã&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;unordered_list&quot; style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list_item&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;il cervello rappresenta solo &lt;strong&gt;il 2% del peso corporeo&lt;/strong&gt;, ma &lt;strong&gt;consuma il 20% dell‚Äôenergia totale giornaliera&lt;/strong&gt; (&quot;&lt;em&gt;The Man Who Tasted Shapes&quot;&lt;/em&gt;, MIT Press, 2003);&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list_item&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;A fine mese mi &lt;strong&gt;sposter√≤ su Substack&lt;/strong&gt;. Per te non cambia nulla. Io invece ho bisogno di &quot;cose&quot; nuove. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tre, due, uno. Si parte.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr style=&quot;color:#5d8e79;height:5px;alignment:center;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;end-caps:square;border:none;background-color:#5d8e79;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:34px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;cosa stai evitando quando scrolli? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Quando ho letto i feedback del questionario della settimana scorsa, ce ne sono stati alcuni che mi hanno fatto riflettere. Altri me li aspettavo. E un paio mi sono sembrati interessanti per crescere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Ma poi √® arrivata una mail. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Tranquilla: non dir√≤ il tuo nome, visto che mi leggi. Dentro c‚Äôera scritto:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;‚ÄúAlessio, la tua newsletter mi sta curando goccia dopo goccia. Settimana dopo settimana.‚Äù&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Continuava.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;‚ÄúLeggendoti da un po‚Äô, tu parli effettivamente al cuore del problema. La distrazione non √® il problema. √à il sintomo. √à il cerotto che metti sulla ferita per non vederla sanguinare.‚Äù&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Ecco, oggi voglio restare l√¨. Su quella frase.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Perch√© se ti sanguina un dito, anche solo il mignolo, succede una cosa molto chiara.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;Vedi il sangue e ti muovi. Vai al lavandino. Disinfetti. Premi. Metti un cerotto. Proteggi.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Non dici: ‚ÄúVabb√®, domani‚Äù.&lt;br&gt;Non apri Instagram per non pensarci.&lt;br&gt;Non ti metti un podcast nelle orecchie mentre il sangue scende.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Agisci perch√© la ferita √® visibile. √à davanti a te. √à reale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Con la mente, invece, facciamo l‚Äôopposto.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;Quando senti un taglietto dentro: &lt;strong&gt;una fitta di solitudine, una paura, una rabbia &lt;/strong&gt;che non vuoi nominare, non corri a disinfettare.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;Corri a coprire. &lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;E lo fai con cose che sembrano innocue. Anzi, normali.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Abbiamo normalizzato il &quot;coprire&quot;. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ascoltiamo un podcast mentre camminiamo. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Scrolliamo i reel in bagno. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mettiamo musica mentre cuciniamo.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Accendiamo Netflix mentre mangiamo.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;√à come se non ci fosse pi√π spazio per respirare con la mente.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;E qui arriva il paradosso: riempiamo ogni vuoto per non sentirlo, poi ci sentiamo intontiti e demotivati.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;E a quel punto pensiamo di avere un problema noi.&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Ma l‚Äôattenzione non √® un interruttore rotto.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;√à un muscolo stanco.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Se lo alleni solo con stimoli veloci, si abitua al veloce e rifiuta il lento.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;‚Äã&lt;br&gt;E il lento √® proprio dove nascono le idee, la presenza, la voglia. &lt;em&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anche la serenit√†.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quindi no, non ti serve un trucco per concentrarti di pi√π.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Ti serve ricostruire un po‚Äô di &lt;strong&gt;silenzio operativo nella giornata&lt;/strong&gt;. Poco. Ma vero.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Certo, rimuovere le notifiche √® importante.&lt;br&gt;Certo, lavorare senza distrazioni per 25 minuti √® utilissimo.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ma il vero cambiamento succede in un altro punto. Quello che eviti.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Succede quando non hai niente da consumare.&lt;br&gt;Quando resti in silenzio.&lt;br&gt;Quando ti riconnetti con te stesso e ti chiedi, senza scappare:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perch√© sto vivendo questo?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;E l√¨ non trovi un assistente che ti risponde.&lt;br&gt;Trovi qualcosa di diverso.&lt;strong&gt; Un‚Äôintelligenza spirituale che ti ascolta.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Non sto parlando di religioni.&lt;br&gt;Sto parlando di limite.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Perch√© quando ti guardi davvero, capisci una cosa semplice:&lt;strong&gt; ogni relazione chiede un prezzo.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;‚Äã&lt;br&gt;Il  giusto prezzo si chiama, attenzione: cura.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;strong&gt;Il prezzo nascosto si chiama distrazione: allontanare da te.&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#000000;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:21px;color:#5d8e79;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;text-align:left&quot; class=&quot;blockquotes&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;blockquotes-line&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;E quando ti allontani, quasi sempre c‚Äô√® di mezzo la paura.&lt;br&gt;‚Äã&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Paura del conflitto.&lt;br&gt;Paura di deludere.&lt;br&gt;Paura di perdere un lavoro, un ruolo, un affetto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;E allora diventi &quot;dipendente&quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Non da una persona soltanto.&lt;br&gt;Dipendente dalla mail che arriva e ti fa tirare un respiro.&lt;br&gt;Dipendente dal calendario pieno che ti fa sentire necessario.&lt;br&gt;Dipendente dal feed che ti distrae quando non vuoi sentire.&lt;br&gt;Dipendente dalla conferma, dalla fuga, dal rumore.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;In questi giorni mi √® tornato in mente un libro, &lt;strong&gt;&quot;Risolvere le cinque ferite&quot; &lt;/strong&gt;di Maria Rosa Fimman√≤. Parla anche di una ferita che oggi il digitale amplifica senza tregua: &lt;strong&gt;la ferita da abbandono.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Quando sei in compagnia stai meglio. Quando resti solo ti si abbassa tutto. E allora tieni un filo sempre acceso: chat aperte, vocali, messaggi, presenza continua.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ma il punto non √® l‚Äôinformazione. √à l‚Äôappoggio.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Presenza. Conferma. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Qualcuno che ti faccia sentire che non sei solo. &lt;br&gt;Non stai delegando un compito. &lt;strong&gt;Stai delegando un bisogno: sentirti che l&apos;altro o l&apos;altra di vede, ti riconosce. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:19px;color:#696969;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5&quot;&gt;Qui entra un punto delicato, ma necessario.&lt;/p&gt;
